    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car starts reliably every morning, there are clear signs of use throughout. The exterior features several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows visible wear on the upholstery and carpets. It is a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility and mechanical reliability over a perfect aesthetic appearance.",
