      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it shows in every single detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
