    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the E46 chassis, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe, a complete VANOS overhaul, and updated rod bearings. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional lock-up, while the suspension retains its original compliance and sharp turn-in characteristics. Presented in collector-grade condition with original paint depth and zero interior bolster wear, this is a turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
